th employers, recruiters, and hiring managers on your behalf. We are not liable for the actions of these individuals or companies and their use of your information is not subject to this Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n	<li>We may share your Personal Information with our contractors and service providers who perform functions on our behalf. For example, we use third parties to provide credit card processing services on our website, and we will disclose your credit card and billing information to such third parties so that they may process your payment on our behalf.</li>\r\n	<li>We also may disclose the information we collect from you in order to comply with the law, a judicial proceeding, court order, or other legal process, such as in response to a subpoena.</li>\r\n	<li>To a buyer or other successor in the event of a merger, divestiture, restructuring, reorganization, dissolution or other sale or transfer of some or all of our assets or stock, whether as a going concern or as part of bankruptcy, liquidation or similar proceeding, in which Personal Information held by us about our Users is among the assets transferred.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USE OF COOKIES AND OTHER TRACKING TECHNOLOGY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use cookies and other tracking technologies to collect information about you and about your use of our website and services. We may combine this information with other personal information we collect from you. We use this information to enhance and personalize your experience while using this website and our services, to track user activities in order to understand how users use our website, and to improve our website and services. We may also use third party vendors to track and analyze website data.&nbsp; We use the data collected by such third parties to help us administer and improve the quality of the website and to analyze website usage. Such third parties may combine the information that we provide about you with other information that they have collected. This Policy does not cover such third parties&#39; use of the data. We use automated devices and applications, such as Google Analytics, to evaluate usage of our website. We may also use other analytic means to evaluate our services. We use these tools to help us improve our services, performance and user experiences. We do not share your personal information with these third parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THIRD PARTY AD NETWORKS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use third parties such as network advertisers to display advertisements on our website. Network advertisers are third parties that display advertisements based on your visits to our website as well as other websites. This enables us and these third parties to target advertisements by displaying ads for products and services in which you might be interested. Third party ad network providers, advertisers, sponsors and/or traffic measurement services may use cookies, JavaScript, web beacons (including clear GIFs), Flash LSOs and other technologies to measure the effectiveness of their ads and to personalize advertising content to you. These third party cookies and other technologies are governed by each third party&#39;s specific privacy policy, not this one. We may provide these third-party advertisers with information about your usage of our website and our services, as well as aggregate or non-personally identifiable information about visitors to our website and users of our service. <strong>&nbsp;</strong> <strong>THIRD PARTY WEBSITES</strong> This website may contain links to other websites. Please note that we have no control over, and are not responsible for, these third party websites. Once you click on one of these links, you are entering a website separate from FindMyProfession.com. We recommend that you review the privacy policies on all such websites as their policies may differ from ours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SECURITY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have implemented&nbsp; reasonable security measures to protect against unauthorized access to and unlawful interception or processing of your Personal Information. Unfortunately, no data transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your Personal Information, we cannot ensure or warranty the security of any such Personal Information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CALIFORNIA RESIDENTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>California residents may choose to request certain information regarding our disclosure of Personal Information to third parties for their direct marketing purposes or choose to opt out of such disclosure. To make a request or to opt out at any time, please contact us at help@findmyprofession.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CHANGES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We may change this Privacy Policy from time to time, and the updated version will be posted on our website in place of the old version. We will also include the date that the currently displayed Privacy Policy took effect to help you determine whether there have been any changes since you last used our website. If we make a material modification to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you by sending an email to the email address you have provided (if any) and by other means where appropriate. If you do not agree with the terms of any updated Privacy Policy, you must immediately cease using our website and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CONTACT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this site, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:help@findmyprofession.com\">help@findmyprofession.com</a> or send mail to: Find My Profession ATTN: Privacy Policy 3753 W Turner Rd. Lodi, CA 95242</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Last Modified: September 22, 2016</strong></p>','','2016-09-30 22:29:20','terms-of-use'),(5,'About Us','About Us: Find My Profession - Six Figure Careers - Mid Career Change','Are you ready for a mid-career change? At Find My Profession we specialize in finding six figure careers for our senior and executive clients. Get hired....','<div id=\"header\">\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center\">We help <span style=\"color:#1fbff0\">YOU</span> get hired</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"body\">\r\n<p>Are you ready for a mid-career change? Whether you aren&#39;t being paid what you deserve or you no longer find fulfillment at work, it&#39;s time to consider a career transition. At Find My Profession we specialize in obtaining six figure careers for our clients. With over 10 years of experience in director careers, VP careers, and executive careers, we have built up the most elaborate network of recruiters and hiring managers across the United States.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Find My Profession we work for you, the job seeker, in order to find you your six figure career. We do this by utilizing our constantly growing network of over 100,000 hiring managers and recruiters, 50+ job sites, and various other proprietary resources. We polish your resume, personally market you, and apply directly to six figure jobs within your industry and location.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In other words, we do all the work for you. Our senior and executive career services are designed for professionals making anywhere from $100,000 - $999,999/year. With our 100% satisfaction guarantee, we commit to working with you to find your six figure career. Never search for a job alone again, let the Professionals do the work for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.findmyprofession.com/coaching-services/career-finder/\">Let&#39;s get started!</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Still have questions? Feel free to <a href=\"https://www.findmyprofession.com/contact-us\"><strong>email/call us today</strong></a>.</p>\r\n</div>','about-us-model-1.png','2016-09-08 13:23:01','about-us'),(6,'Career Finder','Career Finder: Six Figure Jobs for the Perfect Career Transition','Are you looking for a career change? Our career finder service was created to find six figure jobs for our clients anywhere in the U.S.','<div id=\"sub_title\">\r\n<p>Are you in a career transition? At Find My Profession, we professionally manage every aspect of your job search with a focus on six figure careers. We know you&rsquo;ll love our executive career services, that&rsquo;s why we offer a 100% Satisfaction Guarantee.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"steps\">\r\n<h1>1</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Give us a&nbsp;call and&nbsp;tell us what you&#39;re looking for in a career</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>2</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Resume makeover &amp; personal team that finds your job</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>3</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Sit back and relax while the interview requests roll in</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"body\">\r\n<p>Changing careers can be a stressful and time-consuming process. Whether you have gone through a layoff, or you want to move forward in your career, we can help ease the pain with our career finder. With over 50 years of experience in HR, we know the right people, practice the best trends, and most importantly, bring better results than anyone else. We are so confident, our career finder comes with a <strong>100% Satisfaction Guarantee.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Find My Profession specializes in finding six figure careers for professionals in all industries across the United States. This includes Senior Manager careers, Director careers, VP careers, Executive careers, and any other career that offers six-figure jobs. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>The job seeker (YOU) is our only focus</strong>.</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>No, we are not recruiters. No, we are not a staffing agency. We do not take a huge percentage of your salary like recruiters (20% on average). You invest a small, one-time payment (around 1% of your salary), and we&nbsp;do ALL the work for you from the resume and job applications all the way to the interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our career finder brings you tremendous results by utilizing hundreds of industry specific professional groups, over 100,000 professional connections, 90+ job boards, and a variety of other resources. When you add it all up, we have access to over 2.5 million recruiters and hiring managers across the U.S.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The reason our career finder is so successful is simple. Recruiters charge hiring managers around 20% of your annual salary in order to place you in a new role. We charge hiring managers nothing. This allows us to work with (not for) tens of thousands of companies. Instead of spending time signing contracts and gaining new business with the hiring manager, we spend that time working for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Answer me this, if you were a hiring manager, would you prefer to hire:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Option 1) A free referral sent to you by Find My Profession.<br />\r\nOption 2) A lead that would cost you an additional 20% on top of their annual salary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Of course, who wouldn&#39;t select Option 1? This business model gives us the competitive advantage and allows our clients (you) to stand out. Since we don&#39;t work for any hiring managers directly,&nbsp;there are absolutely no limitations on where we can find you a job. Your agenda is our agenda. Removing these limitations exponentially increases your chances of being hired.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So, if you are changing careers and make at least $100,000 per year, our career finder service is your golden ticket to your next job. Give us a <strong><a href=\"https://www.findmyprofession.com/contact-us/\">call today</a></strong> to learn how we can help manage your job search.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Never search for a job alone again. - Find My Profession</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"slider_header_title\">\r\n<h1><strong>Career Finder Service</strong></h1>\r\n</div>','','2016-08-20 01:18:09','career-finder'),(7,'Resume Makeover','Professional Resume Makeover: CV & Resume Services','Did you know that a professional CV and resume optimization could help you land your dream job? Try our resume makeover services and see for yourself!','<div id=\"sub_title\">\r\n<p>Have you ever wondered how you ca