d.... Voil&agrave;! Your resume is complete and ready to impress even the pickiest readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Feel free to give one of our <strong><span style=\"color:#1dbff0\"><a href=\"https://www.findmyprofession.com/contact-us/\" style=\"color: #1dbff0;\">resume optimization experts</a>&nbsp;</span></strong>a call and see what we can do for you. We&rsquo;ve got a complete range of plans for you to select from depending on your seniority level. Check out our senior and executive level resume service and see what we have to offer. &nbsp; If you are tired of running around in search for resume writing services that actually work, then your search ends here! Give us a call now to speak with a professional and let the job-hunt begin!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"packages\">\r\n<p>Senior</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Senior packages are for expected earnings of&nbsp;<strong>$100,000 - $200,000/year</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A 45-minute chat over Skype or phone</li>\r\n	<li>An updated, optimized&nbsp;and redesigned resume from our Senior Resume&nbsp;Experts</li>\r\n	<li>Two rounds of edits</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Executive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Executive packages are for expected earnings of&nbsp;<strong>$200,000+/year</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A 60-minute chat over Skype or phone</li>\r\n	<li>An updated, optimized&nbsp;and redesigned resume from our Executive Resume&nbsp;Experts</li>\r\n	<li>Unlimited resume edits for 2 weeks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','','2016-08-28 00:14:02','resume-makeover'),(8,'Cover Letter Service','Professional Cover Letter | Executive Cover Letter Writing Services','Need help writing a professional cover letter? Our executive cover letter writing services help job seekers write cover letters that get them the job!','<div id=\"sub_title\">\r\n<p>A professional cover letter can show a lot about you as an employee. Having a customized, compelling, and professional cover letter is going to create a positive first impression with your future employer.&nbsp;</p>\